    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/how-much-furthe-can-pound-rise-41796-180126">英镑还有多少上涨空间？</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2018/01/26/how-much-furthe-can-pound-rise-41796/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1516944373967.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">英镑是2018年表现最好的G10货币，这一趋势会持续吗？对于将英镑兑日元作为主要机会这一观点，EFX证券的马丁·阿诺德（Martin Arnold）持谨慎态度。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
                    <span class="article-category-section-date time" data-datetime="2018-01-26T05:26:48+0000">2018-01-26T05:26:48+0000</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>

    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/weekly-fx-technical-41701-180122">五大货币一周技术分析（1月22日-26日）：重点关注日、欧央行的利率决议</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2018/01/22/weekly-fx-technical-41701/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1516612165121.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">上周美国没有重要的经济数据和风险事件，缺乏驱动因素的美元在低位振荡整理。美元指数上周的总体振荡范围在90.30-80之间，本周应关注指数能否突破区间寻得方向。风险事件方面，本周应重点关注日、欧央行的利率决议，英国第四季度GDP和就业数据，美国第四季度GDP和耐用品订单数据等。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
                    <span class="article-category-section-date time" data-datetime="2018-01-22T09:11:58+0000">2018-01-22T09:11:58+0000</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>

    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
