                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2018/01/15/weekly-fx-technical-analysis-41575/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1516005734956.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

