    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/federal-reserve-system-change-41462-180109">重磅炸弹---即将到来的美联储人事变局</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2018/01/09/federal-reserve-system-change-41462/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1515481270937.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">而作为美国的中央银行，美联储从美国国会获得权力，行使制定货币政策和对美国金融机构进行监管等职责。这也使得美联储在全球经济上有着举足轻重的地位，可以说很大程度上左右了全球经济走势。就在下个月，这家有着100多年历史的中央银行的最高领导层将换届，这也是美联储40年来最大规模的人事调整。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
                    <span class="article-category-section-date time" data-datetime="2018-01-09T07:46:52+0000">2018-01-09T07:46:52+0000</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>

    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/fx-weekly-technical-analysis-41444-180108">五大货币一周技术分析（1月8日-12日）：黄金/美元看跌楔形警示回落风险</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2018/01/08/fx-weekly-technical-analysis-41444/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1515400358860.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">上周美联储公布的会议纪要支持逐渐加息预期，但经济数据表现参差不齐其中ISM制造业指数表现强于预期，而ISM非制造业指数和非农增长却意外惨淡。美元并未受到差劲非农等数据的过多打击，衡量美元整体强弱的美指上周跌幅收窄，随着美元指数进入低位的三角形整理，本周的突破方向或决定美元将延续跌势还是迎来反弹。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
