                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/how-to-trade-a-hard-brexit-41340-171228">如果英国硬退欧，交易良机藏在哪？</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2017/12/28/how-to-trade-a-hard-brexit-41340/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1514445927000.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

