    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/trading-ideas/risk-management-41316-171227">有效管理外汇交易风险</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/12/27/risk-management-41316/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1514333466416.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">外汇交易涉及的风险比其它资产类别更高，相应地，回报或损失也可能更大。如何管理风险，很大程度上将决定在货币市场交易中我们能获得怎样的成功。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
