        </div>
    </li>

    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/fx-weekly-technical-analysis-41306-171225">五大货币一周技术分析（12月25日-29日）：美元或振荡整理</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2017/12/25/fx-weekly-technical-analysis-41306/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1514193940816.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">本周的交易时间由于处在圣诞与元旦之间，无论是事件数据等驱动因素还是投资者交投热情可能都很低迷，因此市场波动性也将大打折扣，美元可能进行偏弱的振荡整理。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
                    <span class="article-category-section-date time" data-datetime="2017-12-25T09:25:50+0000">2017-12-25T09:25:50+0000</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>

    <li class="article-category-section-list-item item">
        <div class="article-category-section-item">

            <div class="article-category-copy">
                <span class="article-category-section-title"><a class="primary" href="/zh/technical-analysis/weekly-fx-technical-analysis-41199-171218">五大货币一周技术分析（12月18日-22日）：黄金/美元进一步反弹将面临多重阻力</a></span>

                
                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2017/12/18/weekly-fx-technical-analysis-41199/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1513587879385.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">上周美联储等多家央行公布最新利率决议，同时美国公布了CPI以及零售销售等多项重要数据，然而大量的重要事件并没有引发大的行情。美元上周表现振荡，美元指数上周五几乎收于周初开盘水平。本周关注美国GDP修正值以及PCE通胀数据，由于汇市已经在西方圣诞节前出现明显波动性下降的趋势，这些数据可能只会驱动美元延续振荡整理。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
                    <span class="article-category-section-date time" data-datetime="2017-12-18T09:12:09+0000">2017-12-18T09:12:09+0000</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>

        
        
    

    <li class="item fullwidth">
        
        






